channel.title: Client Trouble
channel.description:
When i change the items inside one of my shops using the shops.cgf and when i start server i get:
Your server is now online! DeltaScape Server. Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "2 416 " at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at ShopHandler.loadShops(ShopHandler.java:86) at ShopHandler.(ShopHandler.java:33) at server.main(server.java:127) Connection from 127.0.0.1:64105 [client-1-Tymoney5456]: Loading Process Completed [Has powers, lag: 2 ms] Connection from 127.0.0.1:64111 [client-2-Tymoney5456]: Loading Process Completed [Has powers, lag: 2 ms] Connection from 127.0.0.1:64112 [client-3-Tymoney5456]: Loading Process Completed [Has powers, lag: 2 ms] Connection from 127.0.0.1:64132 [client-4-Tymoney5456]: Loading Process Completed [Has powers, lag: 1 ms] Connection from 127.0.0.1:64147 [client-5-Tymoney5456]: Loading Process Completed [Has powers, lag: 2 ms] BANNING HOST 127.0.0.1 (flooding) ClientHandler: Rejected 127.0.0.1:64155 ClientHandler: Rejected 127.0.0.1:64168 ClientHandler: Rejected 127.0.0.1:64169 ClientHandler: Rejected 127.0.0.1:64170 ClientHandler: Rejected 127.0.0.1:64171
Does anyone know what happened? i did this to another shop and it worked fine and items appeared. Help would be apreciated If you do view this page please reply, even if you do not know
